dc_title_s: South America, Trinidad and Tobago, Venezuela, Guyana, Galeota Point to Pomeroon River (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: from British Admiralty and U.S. charts to 1984 ; Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Relief shown by spot heights. "Soundings in meters." "Copyright restrictions of the country of origin continue to exist." Inset: Guyana. Includes compilation diagram and index to next larger scale charts. Georeferenced nautical chart. Map no. 24390. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
